xxit / xxit                   Terminates the connection and doesn't save files

   Format:
      ;xxit                   Terminates the connection immediately
      ;xxit <minutes>         Terminates the connection after a delay

   Notes:
      Use this command to terminate the connection immediately, without waiting
         for the world to respond.
      By using this command, you will lose any changes you have made to Axmud's
         stored data. Use the ';exit' command to terminate the connection
         immediately while saving files.
      See also the help for ';abortselfdestruct'.

   User commands:
      xxit
